                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, A</hi> 412). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">Read: "Guildhall, Westminster, February,</hi> 15<hi rend="italic">th,</hi> 1858; <hi rend="italic">Robert Merritt was convicted of larceny. 
Confined Twelve Months "</hi>)—Merritt is the person.</p>
